com.amplifyframework.core.model.annotations

Annotation Type Indexes


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=TYPE)
public @interface Indexes
    Indexes allows an instance of Model to be annotated with multiple Index. The RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME annotation is added to retain Indexes at runtime for the reflection capabilities to work in order to check if this annotation is present for a field of a Model. ElementType.TYPE annotation is added to indicate Indexes annotation can be used only on types (class, interface, enum).

    • Required Element Summary

      Required Elements 
      Modifier and Type Required Element and Description
      Index[] value
      Specify the array of indexes of a Model.
